ID: TC_004

Title: Login user with wrong password

Priority: High

Severity: Critical

Preconditions:
* User registered (Email: vladTest1@gmail.com, Password: vladTest1)
* User not logged in

Test data:
* Email: vladTest1@gmail.com (correct)
* Password: WrongPass123 (incorrect)

Steps: 
1. Navigate to “https://automationexercise.com/login”
2. Enter email in “Email Address” field (vladTest1@gmail.com)
3. Enter wrong password in “Password” field (WrongPass123)
4. Click “Login” button

Expected result:
1. Error message displayed: "Your email or password is incorrect!"
2. Login unsuccessful - no navigation to homepage
3. User remains on /login page (URL unchanged)
4. Login form still accessible for retry

Actual result:

Post-conditions: 
* User remains logged out
* Form available for retry

Status: Not Run